PresentationTable.name: More Time Objects
PresentationTable.Description: -> This folder contains additional time attributes like Calendar time attributes and Julian period numbers.

PresentationColumn.name: Day Of Week
PresentationColumn.Description: Day of Week is an integer and is a value between 1 and 7

PresentationColumn.name: Day Of Month
PresentationColumn.Description: Day of Month is an integer and a value between 1 and 31.

PresentationColumn.name: Day Of Year
PresentationColumn.Description: Day of Year is an integer and a value between 1 and 366.

PresentationColumn.name: Julian Day Num
PresentationColumn.Description: Stores the Julian Day Number as an integer.

PresentationColumn.name: Julian Week Num
PresentationColumn.Description: Stores the Julian Week Number as an integer.

PresentationColumn.name: Julian Month Num
PresentationColumn.Description: Stores the Julian Month Number as an integer.

PresentationColumn.name: Julian Qtr Num
PresentationColumn.Description: Stores the Julian Quarter Number as an integer.
